01:19:37,873 --> 01:19:40,273
What is this for?
The spirits are electrical.

1012
01:19:40,475 --> 01:19:43,239
So we can ground them with the wire.
Exactly.

1013
01:19:51,553 --> 01:19:52,611
Okay, I'm ready.

1014
01:19:52,821 --> 01:19:56,917
Dad, will this work?
Oh, that's great, Daisy. That's great.

1015
01:19:57,125 --> 01:20:00,492
All right, so attach one end
to the radiosonde

1016
01:20:01,696 --> 01:20:03,755
and this end to the tower.

1017
01:20:03,965 --> 01:20:04,989
And then...

1018
01:20:05,200 --> 01:20:07,566
Hope that it works better
than salt and water.

1019
01:20:07,769 --> 01:20:10,260
Don't change the frequency
till I tell you to.

1020
01:20:10,472 --> 01:20:12,030
Wait.

1021
01:20:16,178 --> 01:20:17,509
I still love you.

1022
01:20:17,712 --> 01:20:18,838
I love you too.

1023
01:20:19,915 --> 01:20:21,883
Hey, come here.

1024
01:20:22,083 --> 01:20:23,607
I'm proud of you.

1025
01:20:24,319 --> 01:20:25,946
I love you, Daddy.

1026
01:20:26,154 --> 01:20:27,416
All right.

1027
01:20:27,622 --> 01:20:29,214
I'll be back.

1028
01:20:29,891 --> 01:20:30,949
You better be.

1029
01:21:30,352 --> 01:21:32,286
Mom?

1030
01:21:34,522 --> 01:21:36,422
Oh, my God.

1031
01:21:39,227 --> 01:21:40,626
Change the frequency!

1032
01:21:46,368 --> 01:21:48,199
Change the frequency!

1033
01:21:49,838 --> 01:21:50,964
[GRUNTS]

1034
01:21:57,379 --> 01:21:59,347
[THUNDER CRASHING]

1035
01:22:24,172 --> 01:22:26,140
Oh, come on. Come on.

1036
01:22:29,377 --> 01:22:30,605
[GRUNTS]

1037
01:22:34,082 --> 01:22:36,175
I got it.
Great.

1038
01:22:36,952 --> 01:22:38,419
Oh, my God.

1039
01:22:58,340 --> 01:22:59,932
DAISY:
Oh... What is that?

1040
01:23:02,744 --> 01:23:04,268
Mom!
ASHLEY: Oh, my God.

1041
01:23:21,129 --> 01:23:22,118
DAISY:
It's gone.

1042
01:23:23,598 --> 01:23:25,463
[SPIRIT GRUNTING]

1043
01:23:27,502 --> 01:23:28,867
[TYPING ON KEYBOARD]

1044
01:23:31,406 --> 01:23:32,930
DAISY:
Mom, you got it?

1045
01:23:34,209 --> 01:23:35,767
Go to hell.

1046
01:23:37,245 --> 01:23:39,213
[SPIRIT SHRIEKS]

1047
01:23:40,648 --> 01:23:42,309
Hal!

1048
01:23:42,517 --> 01:23:44,610
[GRUNTING]

1049
01:23:48,323 --> 01:23:50,291
[OVERLAPPING VOICES SCREAMING]

1050
01:23:53,528 --> 01:23:55,496
[GROANING]

1051
01:24:07,442 --> 01:24:08,602
[BOTH GASP]

1052
01:24:11,613 --> 01:24:13,706
Oh, dear God.

1053
01:24:16,918 --> 01:24:18,351
Hal!

1054
01:24:19,921 --> 01:24:21,252
Dad!

1055
01:24:26,961 --> 01:24:28,826
Don't you leave me.

1056
01:24:31,332 --> 01:24:33,800
[COUGHING]

1057
01:24:41,109 --> 01:24:43,634
Does this mean you want me back?

1058
01:24:43,945 --> 01:24:45,378
Mm-hm.

1059
01:24:49,851 --> 01:24:51,341
Really?

1060
01:24:56,491 --> 01:24:58,152
You're grounded.

1061
01:25:18,079 --> 01:25:19,307
Do you think it's over?

1062
01:25:20,348 --> 01:25:22,543
Yeah, I do.

1063
01:25:26,354 --> 01:25:27,753
Can we go home now?

1064
01:25:27,956 --> 01:25:29,753
I don't know. Can we?

1065
01:25:31,092 --> 01:25:35,153
Well, I got a bunch of paperwork to do
back at the office.

1066
01:25:36,064 --> 01:25:37,497
Dad.

1067
01:25:38,666 --> 01:25:41,032
Yeah, let's go home.

